title: Jamie.Duries.Edible.Garden.Design.Delicious.Designs.from.the.Gro
description:
Format: Epub
Genre: Gardening/tutorial
Published: 2014

Book Description: Colorful and practical, an edible garden can radically transform an outdoor space and is an affordable, sustainable source of fresh fruit, vegetables, and herbs. In this hands-on guidebook, internationally renowned home and garden design expert Jamie Durie reveals how to plant, arrange, and maintain an edible garden that works in all climates and in spaces of all shapes and sizes.
